it possible to clear and erase to transparency, instead of the
background color. This transforms layers of type RGB to RGBA, GRAY to
GRAYA, and INDEXED to INDEXEDA.
HELP

    &std_pdb_misc;

    @inargs = (
	{ name => 'layer', type => 'layer',
	  desc => 'The layer' }
